{"tid":1922752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我想屌下同路人","createTime":"2020-03-12T17:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T02:24:39.000Z","uid":224350,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0bfdd0c125c330d33630f48191a95785ff2023","tid":1922752,"uid":224350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"你見到標題想入嚟屌鳩我就啱㗎啦<br />\n因為好多人都做緊屌同路人嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我都睇唔過眼啲人做咗少少嘢，<br />\n自覺心安理得就算數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人的確係要屌醒，但屌嘅同時應該比埋改善嘅方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得個句不完美，可接受，要改善<br />\n仲有不分化不割席？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35kzwGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35kzwGW.jpg&h=2c97430a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但嗰啲日日剩係識打卡黃店就當自己任務完成嘅人，有冇諗過你仲有好多嘢可以做到<br />\n<br />\n1.download香城online <br />\n做晒啲任務佢！<br />\n幫手retweet！黃色youtube圈CLS！檢舉KOL100！仲有好撚多，down完自己睇！<br />\n<br />\n2.認清敵人<br />\n屌同路人唔係唔得，但屌之前諗下會唔會係無必要嘅情況下樹敵。<br />\n依個問題最近都講過好多次，但講完大家都係繼續屌。<br />\n<br />\n黃色圈，不論係經濟圈定係YOUTUBER圈<br />\n都被經常批鬥真黃/偽黃；深黃/淺黃。<br />\n我就覺得，只要佢話自己係黃，冇用黃嘅名嚟食人血饅頭，就唔應該拒諸門外。<br />\n的確，可能有啲舖或youtuber 係為咗錢先話自己係黃，但如果佢冇食人血饅頭、冇實際做出對對家有好處嘅事，又出面表態支持我哋，其實就代表我哋依個黃色圈成功咗。<br />\n<br />\n可以睇下一本愛爾蘭共和軍作戰手冊叫《綠書》，入面有講點辨清敵人。有tg channel keep住更新依本書啱用嘅翻譯同革命上嘅知識，係革命嘅同時都要識多啲嘢備戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0rrnM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0rrnM3.png&h=13af9dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tr5PkyK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftr5PkyK.png&h=f48c81d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYg67dL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYg67dL.png&h=6f6c2890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《香港革命指南》<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=31f28b6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual</a><br />\n<br />\n3.流動文宣<br />\nPrint張文宣加個Blu Tack 上巴士就得。<br />\n大家都肯做嘅話，一人一日一張都夠做。<br />\n都覺得有風險嘅，帶支marker 喺出面爆石個陣寫2句囉。<br />\n<br />\n可以做嘅就做盡佢。<br />\n<br />\n4.不斷升級<br />\n屌你，以為做晒上面就夠？夠你老母呀夠<br />\n好撚多嘢要做<br />\n記住你自己係抗爭者，我哋要不停改善同進步<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSFop3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSFop3a.jpg&h=1295bed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民罷工全民勇武<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvnJ9tg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvnJ9tg.jpg&h=341f30f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tR2J9th.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtR2J9th.jpg&h=39f96369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9691fd0d3a172604ecb93f1ba6e103ea0a12a3d1","tid":1922752,"uid":71195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"幫你推 依家呢個時勢係要做多一步先得"},{"pid":"f31587e3829b4b32d425d54b0c74696f3b0673f3","tid":1922752,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"不是要獨立<br />\n而是要脫離中共管治<br />\n團結中港台中華民族"},{"pid":"760892946ab359721c77b07f3017f623cca0896c","tid":1922752,"uid":224350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9691fd0d3a172604ecb93f1ba6e103ea0a12a3d1","tid":1922752,"uid":71195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"幫你推 依家呢個時勢係要做多一步先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"係，好多人覺得自己已經做夠，其實一日未光復到香港，就永遠都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24893dd9998a5d825af1eaf222a90f68b65b4bf1","tid":1922752,"uid":347723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"巴打個post好正👍🏻<br />\n多謝有做功課嘅你"},{"pid":"310a9